    <h1>User Intent (Search Intent)</h1>
    <p class="description">The underlying goal behind a search query. Matching your content to the right intent is the <strong>highest-leverage on-page SEO decision</strong> you can make — more impactful than keyword density, meta tags, or word count alone.</p>
